---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Espacio Inteligente" description="Espacio Inteligente: tested home hacks and smart living tips backed by data. Meet the author.">
  <section class="about">
    <div class="container about__inner">
      <h1>About Espacio Inteligente</h1>

      <div class="about-author">
        <h2>Vladys Z.</h2>
        <p class="author-subtitle">App Developer · Professional Chef · Smart Living Enthusiast</p>
      </div>

      <p>I'm Vladys — professional chef and app developer who's spent years optimizing both kitchens and code. EspacioInteligente brings that optimization mindset to your entire home.</p>

      <p>As a chef, my kitchen is my lab — I know which hacks actually save time and which are just TikTok nonsense. As a developer, I test everything with data before recommending it.</p>

      <p>Every tip on this site has been tested, measured, and verified. No clickbait, no affiliate-pushed gadgets — just what actually works.</p>

      <h2>Why This Blog?</h2>
      <p>I started Espacio Inteligente because I was tired of home tips that sound great but don't hold up in practice. As someone who spends hours in the kitchen daily and codes automation tools for fun, I wanted a place where every recommendation is backed by real testing and real data.</p>

      <h2>My Promise</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Tested tips</strong> — Every hack has been personally tested and measured for real results</li>
        <li><strong>Zero products to sell</strong> — I don't promote expensive gadgets or affiliate-pushed products</li>
        <li><strong>Personal experience</strong> — I share what I've actually tried in my own home and kitchen</li>
        <li><strong>Free forever</strong> — All knowledge is free and accessible</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Also on YouTube</h2>
      <p>I post daily home and kitchen tips on <a href="https://youtube.com/@EspacioInteligente" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@EspacioInteligente</a> — quick, practical content for smarter living.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>vladys.z96@gmail.com</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about { padding: 3rem 0; }
  .about__inner { max-width: var(--content-width); }
  .about__lead {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
  .about-author { margin-bottom: 2rem; }
  .author-subtitle { font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--color-text-light); margin-top: 0.25rem; }
  .about h2 { margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
  .about p { margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--color-text-light); line-height: 1.7; }
  .about ul { padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .about li { margin-bottom: 0.5rem; color: var(--color-text-light); }
</style>
